  dialogueLines:
  - Hey! We've met before
  - Do you still remember me?
  - I am just here to guide you to the final stage in this world
  - Now use all you have and try to defeat the Stone Boss!
  - It's fine if you loss, I'll use my power to bring you back to this point
  - and also to this time
  - Good luck now!
  - It's like the novel storyline, right?
  - The start is also the end
